QuestData.Title: Pet Up
QuestData.Description:
It sounds like some group of pet poachers are up to no good in the Eye of Azshara. My supply manager's flight path takes him right over that area!
Zantini and his pets, Strigfellow and Speedy IV, were bringing back a rare murloc pet, along with some other pets and supplies.
$n, please find Zantini and his pets. Help them out. Then we can try to recover the pets and the supplies.
QuestData.LogDescription: Find and help Zantini and his pets along the coast of the Eye of Azshara.
